<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sweet Delights Cake Shop</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles and Dynamic Pink/Blue Background */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffdee9 0%, #b5fffc 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ff6b81;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #48dbfb;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #ff4757;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #57606f;
        }

        /* Content Sections */
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ff4757;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #48dbfb;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Flavors Grid (Clickable Cards) */
        .flavor-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .flavor-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        /* Dynamic Clickable Background Effect (Pink & Blue) */
        .flavor-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .flavor-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        /* Give alternate cards pink/blue click accents */
        .flavor-card.pink-click:active {
            background-color: #ffdee9;
            border-color: #ff6b81;
        }

        .flavor-card.blue-click:active {
            background-color: #b5fffc;
            border-color: #48dbfb;
        }

        .flavor-card h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #2f3542;
        }

        /* Contact Button */
        .btn-contact {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff6b81;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 107, 129, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-contact:hover {
            background-color: #48dbfb;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(72, 219, 251, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-contact:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #747d8c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#quality">Best Quality</a>
            <a href="#flavors">Flavors</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section (Cake Shop Name) -->
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Sweet Delights</h1>
        <p>Baking your dreams come true, one slice at a time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>Sweet Delights</strong>! We are a passionate, family-owned bakery dedicated to crafting the most delicious and beautiful cakes for your special moments. Every cake is baked fresh from scratch using traditional recipes and a modern touch of love.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Best Quality Section -->
        <section id="quality">
            <h2>Our Best Quality Guarantee</h2>
            <p>We believe that a great cake starts with premium ingredients. That is why we commit to:</p>
            <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 15px auto; text-align: left; line-height: 1.6;">
                ✨ 100% Organic & fresh dairy products<br>
                ✨ No artificial preservatives or additives<br>
                ✨ Hand-crafted designs customized to perfection<br>
                ✨ Baked fresh on the day of delivery
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Cake Flavors Section (Clickable) -->
        <section id="flavors">
            <h2>Our Signature Flavors</h2>
            <p><em>Click on a flavor card below to select your favorite!</em></p>
            
            <div class="flavor-grid">
                <!-- Card 1 (Pink Click Accent) -->
                <div class="flavor-card pink-click" onclick="alert('You selected: Classic Strawberry Vanilla!')">
                    <h3>🍓 Strawberry Vanilla</h3>
                    <p>Layers of fluffy vanilla sponge filled with fresh strawberry compote and light whipped cream.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 (Blue Click Accent) -->
                <div class="flavor-card blue-click" onclick="alert('You selected: Royal Chocolate Fudge!')">
                    <h3>🍫 Royal Chocolate</h3>
                    <p>Rich, decadent Belgian chocolate layers smothered in a smooth chocolate ganache frosting.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3 (Pink Click Accent) -->
                <div class="flavor-card pink-click" onclick="alert('You selected: Velvet Red Velvet!')">
                    <h3>🧁 Classic Red Velvet</h3>
                    <p>Traditional deep red cocoa cake paired beautifully with our signature tangy cream cheese frosting.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Section -->
        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Order Now</h2>
            <p>Ready to bring sweetness to your celebration? Give us a call or tap below to dial directly!</p>
            <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
            <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="btn-contact">📞 Call to Place Order</a>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Sweet Delights Cake Shop. Built with love.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
